title.rendered: Importance of Entrepreneurial Mindset with Branded by Women Panel Part 2

content.rendered:
Podcast: Play in new window | Download (Duration: 26:08 — 23.9MB)

Subscribe: Spotify | Email | RSS

Tiffany Hepburn is the founder and CEO of “Eat, Sleep Amazon”. Listen to her speak on what to do with Amazon suspensions, mindset, and about her journey on overcoming her challenge with Lyme disease.

Jelena Nuhanovic owns a PPC agency with her husband. She talks about how everything is possible when you are ready to sacrifice for them. 

If you want to learn How to Develop an Entrepreneurial Mindset, click here.

 

You’ll Learn:

  • How to deal with the challenge of balancing business vs. kids.
  • Importance of being mentally and fully present for anything that you’re doing.
  • Tips on mental mastery of being an entrepreneur.
  • How not to feel guilty for taking time off for yourself.
  • Overcoming business struggles while thriving.
